<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.10">
<l>maṉṉavaṉ toṇṭaiyar kōṉvaṇaṅkum nīḷmuṭi mālaiva yiramēkaṉ</l>
<l>taṉvali taṉpukaḻ cūḻntakacci yaṭṭapu yakarat tātitaṉṉai</l>
<l>kaṉṉinaṉ māmatiḷ maṅkaivēntaṉ kāmaru cīrkkali kaṉṟikuṉṟā</l>
<l>viṉṉicai yālcoṉṉa ceñcolmālai yēttaval lārkkiṭam vaikuntamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Vaikuṇṭha is the place for those who can praise</l>
<l rend="indent">this garland of fine words composed with flawless sweet music</l>
<l>By Kalikaṉṟi of desired esteem, king of Maṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">with excellent, large, impenetrable walls,</l>
<l>To the primal one in the house of the eight-armed [lord] in Kacci</l>
<l rend="indent">where circulate the fame and power</l>
<l>Of Vayiramēkaṉ, with garlands on his high crown,</l>
<l rend="indent">to whom the ruler, the king of the Toṇṭais, bows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
